These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, cherry, artichoke, onion
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, disco, r&b, pop
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, thai, indonesian, british
4 different pets are kept: snake, lizard, hedgehog, goat
 1. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 2. the person eating strawberry is in an even position##4
 3. the indian is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
 4. the indonesian is on the right of the person eating onion##1
 5. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
 6. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
 7. the thai is the person eating artichoke##1
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the snake is between the owner of the goat and the fan of pop##2
10. the person eating strawberry is the owner of the goat##1
11. the fan of r&b is the person eating onion##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | artichoke  | strawberry    | onion    | cherry   |
| Music-Genre   | disco     | classical   | r&b       | pop    |
| Nationality   | thai | indian | british    | indonesian |
| Pet           | lizard | goat       | snake | hedgehog     |

