.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: corn, tomato, apple, plum
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, filmmaking, fishing, camping
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, australian, british, indonesian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, badminton, basketball, cricket
 1. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4
 2. the australian is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person eating apple##1
 4. the person eating tomato is the brazilian##1
 5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person eating corn##1
 6. the brazilian is on the left or right of the british##3
 7. the person eating plum is on the right of the person eating apple##1
 8. the indonesian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
 9. the british is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating apple is in an odd position##4
11. the british is the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Food          | corn  | tomato    | apple     | plum       |
| Hobby         | fishing | camping | gardening   | filmmaking |
| Nationality   | british | brazilian   | australian   | indonesian    |
| Sport         | basketball | cricket  | snowboarding | badminton   |

