.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, 7up, lemonade, cola
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, dressmaker, software-developer, nurse
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, spanish, indian, russian
4 different pets are kept: horse, hamster, rat, cat
 1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the journalist##3
 2. the spanish is the software-developer##1
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 4. the journalist is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 5. the person drinking 7up is the nurse##1
 6. the person drinking cola is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 7. the owner of the horse is the russian##1
 8. the nurse is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the turkish##1
10. the owner of the horse is the person drinking lemonade##1
11. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | lemonade   | cola    | 7up      |
| Job           | software-developer | journalist | dressmaker | nurse     |
| Nationality   | spanish      | russian   | turkish   | indian |
| Pet           | cat         | horse       | rat  | hamster       |

