.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, soy-milk, lemonade, juice
There 4 different types of food: banana, carrot, pineapple, pomegranate
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, filmmaking, writing, camping
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, golf, swimming, water-polo
 1. the person drinking tea is the person eating banana##1
 2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 3. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
 4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an even position##4
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 6. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 7. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 8. the person eating carrot is on the left or right of the person eating pomegranate##3
 9. the person who's sport is swimming is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
11. the person drinking lemonade is the person eating pomegranate##1
12. the person eating pomegranate is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | juice       | lemonade   | tea   | soy-milk   |
| Food       | carrot        | pomegranate | banana    | pineapple       |
| Hobby      | camping | filmmaking    | writing  | collecting |
| Sport      | golf  | swimming  | biathlon | water-polo    |

