.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, peach, blueberry, kale
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, collecting, singing
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, lawyer, electrician, doctor
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, rugby, climbing, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person eating kale##2
 3. the electrician is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 4. the lawyer is the person eating asparagus##1
 5. the architect is on the left or right of the lawyer##3
 6. the person who's hobby is cooking is in an even position##4
 7. the person eating peach is the architect##1
 8. the person who's hobby is collecting is the lawyer##1
 9. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
10. the lawyer is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
11. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left or right of the person eating blueberry##3
12. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Food    | blueberry    | kale      | asparagus          | peach    |
| Hobby   | drawing | singing       | collecting | cooking |
| Job     | doctor     | electrician      | lawyer     | architect |
| Sport   | rugby   | weightlifting | climbing        | biathlon   |

