.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, soy-milk, cola, coffee
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, strawberry, zucchini, kiwi
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, country, house, d&b
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, american, japanese, russian
 1. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 3. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
 4. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan of d&b is between the japanese and the fan of country##2
 7. the fan of house is the person eating zucchini##1
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is the person eating zucchini##1
 9. the american is on the far right##1
10. the australian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Beverage      | cola  | soy-milk    | almond-milk       | coffee       |
| Food          | kiwi    | zucchini | strawberry | nectarine     |
| Music-Genre   | metal | house        | d&b    | country   |
| Nationality   | australian  | japanese      | russian    | american |

