 3. the indian is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 4. the person watching mystery movies is in an odd position##4
 5. the canadian is on the right of the malaysian##1
 6. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
 7. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
