 9. the owner of the pony is between the indian and the person watching satire movies##2
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
11. the person who's hobby is baking is in an even position##4
12. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3

