.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: pear, cauliflower, kale, blueberry
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, romance, superhero, musical
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, punk, electronic, disco
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, golf, ice-hockey, weightlifting
 1. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in an even position##4
 3. the fan of country is between the person watching romance movies and the person who's sport is golf##2
 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
 5. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
 6. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person eating kale##1
 7. the fan of disco is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person watching romance movies##1
 9. the person eating pear is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
11. the person eating pear is on the far left or far right##3
12. the fan of punk is on the left of the person eating kale##1
13. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |      4       |
| Food          | pear     | kale      | blueberry  | cauliflower        |
| Movie-Genre   | romance     | superhero | epic | musical      |
| Music-Genre   | punk      | country        | disco        | electronic        |
| Sport         | weightlifting | skateboarding    | golf      | ice-hockey |

