 3. the accountant is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's sport is swimming##2
 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the chinese##1
 5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person drinking mirinda##1
 6. the colombian is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person drinking water is on the far right##1
 8. the chinese is on the right of the colombian##1
 9. the pilot is on the left of the accountant##1
10. the analyst is in an even position##4
11. the indian is the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
