.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, coffee, cola, tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, puzzles, collecting, sudoku
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, musical, family, martial-arts
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, snowboarding, golf, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
 2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 4. the person watching musical movies is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching family movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
10. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
11. the person watching martial-arts movies is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | cola       | coffee | lemonade        | tea        |
| Hobby         | sudoku | collecting       | cooking | puzzles |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts     | musical        | superhero    | family      |
| Sport         | snowboarding     | golf    | weightlifting | parkour   |

