.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, reggae, funk, rock
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, mexican, italian, german
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, surfing, badminton, skateboarding
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, roller, quad-bike, van
 1. the fan of rock is the person who's sport is badminton##1
 2. the person who's sport is badminton is between the canadian and the german##2
 3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
 4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the mexican##1
 5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 6. the fan of reggae is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 7. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
 8. the german is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
10. the canadian is in an even position##4
11. the canadian is on the far right##1
12. the fan of classical is on the right of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | reggae      | classical | rock     | funk        |
| Nationality   | italian | german  | mexican     | canadian |
| Sport         | surfing    | rowing | badminton      | skateboarding |
| Transport     | van | roller     | quad-bike | trike       |

 